text:
Turn the optimization problem into a optimization model graph by using Mermaid.js Live Editor Syntax. Include the Entities, Attributes, Relationships, Goals, Conditions. Use the following colors for the different classes
%% Class Definitions
classDef entity fill:#d1b3ff,stroke:#333;
classDef variable fill:#99e699,stroke:#333;
classDef goal fill:#99ccff,stroke:#333;
classDef constraint fill:#ff9999,stroke:#333;
classDef relationship fill:#ffe066,stroke:#333;
